For bigger herds, you need 
you need to force yourself 

124
00:07:17,082 --> 00:07:21,944
to count only the animals 
present inside counting path. 

125
00:07:22,651 --> 00:07:25,889
The meteorological conditions 
and visibility 

126
00:07:26,099 --> 00:07:29,124
can also greatly affect 
the counting performance.

127
00:07:29,963 --> 00:07:33,850
The experience of a people 
is essential to avoid 

128
00:07:34,086 --> 00:07:37,286
identification.mistakes 
and to quickly being able

129
00:07:37,521 --> 00:07:40,546
to estimate the number
of animal present. 

130
00:07:40,732 --> 00:07:43,319
You also need 
to take into account that 

131
00:07:43,518 --> 00:07:47,305
tiredness greatly affects attention 
after a while. 

132
00:07:47,550 --> 00:07:51,562
Of course, you would need test
of the ability of the observers 

133
00:07:51,780 --> 00:07:56,905
to fly  without getting sick
in often harsh conditions.

134
00:07:57,550 --> 00:07:59,887
Finally, since it's a low 
level flight

135
00:08:00,124 --> 00:08:02,011
in a quite hostile environment, 

136
00:08:02,186 --> 00:08:04,023
you need to have a prepared team

137
00:08:04,146 --> 00:08:06,084
to the possibility 
of an engine failure, 

138
